<h1>Austin Kleon</h1>

<h2><a href="/">/now</a>: <a href="http://austinkleon.com/now/">austinkleon.com/now</a></h2>

<h2>Location:</h2>
<p>
Austin
TX
United States
</p>

<h2>Professional title:</h2>
<p>
I'm a writer who draws.
</p>

<h2>What do you do?</h2>
<p>
I make art with words and books with pictures.
</p>

<h2>Why?</h2>
<p>
I'm a professional writer so I can be a professional reader — what I really like to do is sit around all day with a stack of books.
</p>

<h2>Recent thought or epiphany?</h2>
<p>
Problems of output are usually problems of input.
</p>

<h2>What should we read?</h2>
<p>
This year: Jon Ronson's “SO YOU'VE BEEN PUBLICLY SHAMED”
</p>

